{"tid":1641351,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"全球戰線 -- 價值觀之戰","createTime":"2019-10-09T10:11:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T10:12:29.000Z","uid":90464,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"94d55d2b4bcff0b2722b9f1281c706a173a2938b","tid":1641351,"uid":90464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:11:25.000Z","msg":"NBA 和 Blizzard 事件爆發後，西方文明+香港 與 中共国之間的衝突，已經不是經濟利益這麼簡單，而是進入人民 vs 人民的<span style=\"color: red;\">價值觀之爭</span>！<br />\n<br />\n香港人繼承大英傳統，亦見慣北方民眾精神面貌，相信對兩種不同價值觀十分熟悉。<br />\n奇怪的是，同一套政治術語：自由、民主、人權、法治，放在普世價值和中国价值，竟然可以有完全不同的解讀邏輯！這可能是黃藍之間（或世界與中共之間）經常雞同鴨講／對牛彈琴的原因。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">普世價值中的自由</span>＝人民擁有言論、新聞、結社、信仰、學術等自由 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">中国价值中的自由</span>＝我有自由喜欢做什么也可以，不用你管 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">普世價值中的民主</span>＝人民擁有選舉權與被選舉權 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">中国价值中的民主</span>＝你做什么之前有问过我们（主流意見）吗？  <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">普世價值中的人權</span>＝人民擁有生存、自由、公正、尊嚴、自決等權利 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">中国价值中的人权</span>＝我有吃喝玩乐的权利（和侵犯你权利的权利） <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">普世價值中的法治</span>＝人民受法律約束及保障，政府受法律制衡 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">中国价值中的法治</span>＝总之犯法就不对，政府做的一定对 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（咦我的房子呢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n還有值得注意，普通話中，權利和權力，法治和法制，是同音的，混淆很正常。<br />\n明白這些差異，我們就 ready to fight this battle!"},{"pid":"9017b8a9fd66c0112ca0c7714d38b038ddf4795c","tid":1641351,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:11:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">國際戰線要人!！</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">呢排國際上發生左幾單重要打<br />\nNBA、south park 、暴雪、red bull <br />\n大家點可以呢個時候懶！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>係時候要世界明白中國有幾醜惡!</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">國際戰線！全球抗共！</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n任務：<br />\n1. Twitter 戰線 請用Tg入面既Twitter help<br />\n2 YouTube 英文短片<br />\n3. Reddit戰線</span></span> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">我地只有令全世界明白香港係幫自由世紀抵擋邪惡國家既先鋒，先可以令世人支持我地！<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d988927f48adb4ae5e7f29abeb91e5b9b1727afa","tid":1641351,"uid":90464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:11:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W4hSYkW.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW4hSYkW.gif&h=b2bc3a83&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3cbe196603aeb7152cd1142316f1f669f2e78c42","tid":1641351,"uid":90464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:12:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W4hSYkW.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW4hSYkW.gif&h=b2bc3a83&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W4hSYkW.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW4hSYkW.gif&h=b2bc3a83&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f1954926449307933936bc614a0b9ac53e6feaa8","tid":1641351,"uid":90464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:12:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/haD2Esj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"ht